	   <tr><td colspan=2>people are always askin me about this stuff.. twinking, buying, and questing for lower lvl items to mid lvl items.. well heres a small list of stuff to obtain.. the total cost of all these items is anywhere from 0 - 3k pp depending on what you want.. but it will take your int based gnome at i believe 133 to 185 if you were to obtain just this list.. theres many other quests that if you want i can go over you with.. just ask me to .. ive more then likely done them.. and many other items ive bought n obtained as well.. anyway these were the items.. i ended up with by lvl 30.. this post was originally in response to a post on july 7th but i thought id put it at the top.. so all the newer guys not reading the whole post can also see and get an idea of things =)<br>good luck !!!<br><br>&quot;this was noted july 18th&quot;<br>this is for everyone.. &quot;twinking your wiz while your lvl 30&quot; by taygarr lilredlooter <br>hehe <br><br>first off.. i know money isnt exactly flowing through your wallets right now.. well get used to it.. most people never see a ton of it =P lol.. <br>but! there are some good inexpensive items to pick up in ec .. or do the quests for!!!! <br><br>1. stien of moguk - this is a 10int item and can be bought for around 350pp usually.. VERY cheap <br>reason its so cheap is cause u can quest for it as well.. and its a pretty simple quest to <br><br>2. batskull earrings - 5int each not lore and you can get these off of oowamp in timerous deep.. hes a ogre shammy .. does buff himself with sow but u wont have any adds.. hes pretty easilly killable with 3 people in the 30s spawns every 5 min or so.. orr you can buy them for about 500 each.. sometimes cheaper .. i still wear these at lvl 55.. not a bad item <br><br>3. 3-5 int rings -&nbsp;&nbsp;rings from this caliber are very easy to obtain a three int ring can usually be bought for about 50pp 5int for about 300.. not terribly hard though. Another one you can do is the band of rochite nife.. its a 3int ring you get in quenyos for a pretty darn easy quest.. recomended lvl is only 9.. this one however i believe is lore.. correct me if im wrong <br><br>4. robe - this ones a lil tougher.. if you have friends in the game youll probably get one of these for free lol.. most people do give out robes .. they are the one item on a wizzy that appeals to people and they see .. robe with 5int on it can be bought for about 500 bucks .. places to aquire a robe.. might be a lil higher then lvl 30 .. blackened cyrstaline robes, crystaline robes, ghostly robes, are some of the more common robes seen .. see if u can score one of these from a friend wizzy.. or friend in the game.. casters tend to carry extra clothes =P <br><br>5. woven brass bracer - 3int 50pp .. very easy to obtain. <br><br>6. gatorscale sleeves - this item is a 4int item that can be obtained off of the accient croc in upper guk.. again this one might be alil tough for you to solo at lvl 30 i dont think you can do it.. but if you can get a few friends to help or maybe just get one lvl 40 person to help you should be perfectly fine .. these sleeves go for about 400pp <br><br>7. main mellee item - this one kinda sux.. the first chance your going to have at a nice item thats not given to you.. or you dont spend 3k on is the staff of wheel. 10int.. nice staff.. 1hb so u can wear it and stien same time.. unfortunetly i recommend lvl 24 to start the quest.. or a very very good guide specially since you have to goto lower guk for one of the rods.. <br>other mellee items are various.. i cant quite think of a quest you can do for a good one right now.. ill have to look it up hmmm <br><br>8. impskin gloves - these drop in Sol A off of a imp (be warned if you never seen imp they look like your familair hehe.. so no ur fam is not mad at you lol) named kindle.. he spawns not terribly far from the enterance.. but get a spawn map off of www.graffe.com for him.. they go for anywhere from 400 - 800 depending on the mood of the punk that has em it seems.. casters belts n gloves can be hard to get.. so these are very nice item to aquire. kindle isnt to tough.. at lvl 32 me and 2 others took him down quite a few times and scored the gloves for my wizzy.. so your ranger n a couple friends same lvl shouldnt have a problem.. he is a rare spawn.. isnt always up.. so be patient.. or hit ec n buy the suckas <br><br>9. batskull head - 3int this is another item that is found on oowamp same time as your getting your batskulls you can get this item to.. its pretty easy to buy to .. only sells for around 75pp to 150pp.. <br><br>10. as far as cape, boots, leggings, and face, it might be hard to find a quest to get these.. you can look for non int items for these for the time being though.. like dex items or agi items or resistance items.. you wont really need the resist until your quite a higher lvl but.. always nice to acquire an put in bank for later! <br><br>i think im pretty much outta ideas.. i knowwww theres other wizzys out there that are like.. oh oh oh taygarr you missed thissss one! lol.. so speak up.. list it if you know it.. any quests under lvl 30 that these guys can acquire for their wizzies? .. reply here.. and good luck with you wizzies guys.. take care! <br><br>taygarr <br>wiz of the 55th season <br>the seventh hammer <br><br>&quot;laurie got affended when i used the word &quot;puke&quot; <br>but to me thats what her dinner tasted like&quot;<br>&nbsp;<br>WIZROG!!!!!!!!</td></tr>
