	   <tr><td colspan=2>Something that often goes overlooked as a wizard chest item is Shardtooth's Flayed Skin. This item has been farmed so much for so long, and the demand is so low, that it can be had for cheap; often 50-100pp on Morell-Thule. It has 14ac, 35hp, and 35 mana...this is awesome for a low to mid-level int caster! For comparison, a Crystal Covered Shroud, with its 4 intelligence, often sells for twice as much, even though 4 intelligence will only surpass 35 mana when you hit level 45...that's a long time. Plus, it actually looks good on Erudites ^_^ \/<br><br>Teriuk Blackarrow<br>Warrior<br>Morell-Thule<br>&nbsp;<br>Teriuk Blackarrow<br>Warrior<br>Morell-Thule</td></tr>
