	   <tr><td colspan=2>As far as the back slot is concerned, you can try the Cloak of the Forlorn, (+2AC, -3Wis, +3Int, +1vsMg, +5Mana, +0.70Wt.)&nbsp;&nbsp;This is dropped by Prince Bragnar in the Warrens.  Bragnar is about a 20th level SK class kobold.<br><br>For Wrists, there's also Polished Bone Bracers, which add +3 to both Int and Wis, which offsets the -3 wis of the cloak.  These drop off of Evil Eyes in East Karana and the Gorge of King Xorbb.  A group of low-20's should be able to handle them fairly well.<br>&nbsp;<br>Arjaizen Izrhume<br>40th Circle Wizard of Erudin<br>Fallen Wolves</td></tr>
